<div type="letter">
<pb facs="1361572" n="1"/>
    <p><lb/>Illustriss.<hi rend="sup">o</hi> et Celeberr.<hi rend="sup">o</hi> Viro
                              <lb/>Amico Vero 
        <lb/><rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-119166895">Nicolao Bernoulli</rs> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-102552517">Petrus <abbr>Ant.<hi rend="sup">us</hi></abbr> Michelotti</rs>
                              <lb/><abbr>S. P. D.</abbr> </p>
<p><lb/>Mihi gaudeo Te incolumem istuc pervenisse;
                              <lb/>quod aut<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> id mihi significaveris gratias
                              <lb/>ago maximas, uti etiam quod animi Tui gene<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>rosissimi atque humilitatis virtute ornatissimi
                              <lb/>benignitate ductus repetere volueris gratiar<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice>
                              <lb/>action<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> de beneficiis; qu<subst><del>a</del><add>o</add></subst>r<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> summ<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> comparat<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice>
                              <lb/>ad maxima tua merita, fateor esse <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>qual<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice>
                              <lb/>nihilo. Ceter<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> scias velim, me ubique locorum,
                              <lb/>nulloque non tempore non tant<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> defensurum
                              <lb/>(si opus fuerit) Tuam existimation<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> uti meam
                              <lb/>ipsam, ver<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> eti<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> pugnatur<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> pro eadem
                              <lb/>tuenda si id necessitas postularet. Amiciti<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> nos<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> conveniet semper <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118520814">Ciceroniana</rs> qu<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> tu nosti
                              <lb/>de Amicitia definitio. Ornatissimus Amicus noster
    <lb/><rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-117596027">Bernardinus Zendrinus</rs> jubet ut Tibi salut<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice>
                              <lb/>plurim<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> mitt<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice>, Tibique signific<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice>, ips<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> <subst><del><gap/></del><add>gravi</add></subst><pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>ter tulisse Tu<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> discess<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice>; seque parat<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> semper
                              <lb/>futur<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> ad mandata Tua exequenda, et ad bene<lb break="no"/>dicend<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> de Te, deque tuo summo Ingenio. Expecta<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tas ab Illustrissimo <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118509969">Patruo</rs> Tuo <rs type="letter" key="B_991170515151405501">litteras</rs> per <rs type="place" key="place_VER-tirola">Tyrolim</rs>
                              <pb facs="1361573" n="2"/>
<lb/>uti sperab<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice>, heri non accepi. Spero crastina die
    <lb/>via <rs type="place" key="place_GEO-3182164">Bergomi</rs> ad me esse deferendas, quod mihi maxi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>mi esset solatii. Nam non par<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> turbatus sum quod
    <lb/>heri easd<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> illas <rs type="letter" key="B_991170515151405501">literas</rs> non acceperim. Si igitur
                              <lb/>accipiam crastina die, sine mora ad Te mittam
                              <lb/>eas, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> erunt pro Temetipso. Salutabo tuo no<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>mine <abbr>Illustriss.<hi rend="sup"><choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice></hi></abbr> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118901125">Joseph<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> Smith</rs> necnon <abbr>D.<hi rend="sup"><choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice></hi></abbr> <rs type="person" key="GND">West</rs>,
                              <lb/>qui eti<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> gravissime tulerunt quod hinc discesse<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>ris. Fautoribus, et Promotoribus Tuis offer<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice>
                              <lb/>debit<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> venerationis cult<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice>, ipsisque dicam Te
                              <lb/>memor<choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice> futur<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> de illor<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> Optima erga Te
    <lb/>voluntate. Repeto hodie <rs type="letter" key="B_991170515151605501">litteras</rs> ad <abbr>Celeber.<hi rend="sup"><choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice></hi></abbr> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118509969">Pa<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tru<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice></rs> Tu<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> dubitans quod neque crastina die
    <lb/>forte ad me<del> non</del> deferantur<del>,</del> ejus <rs type="letter" key="B_991170515151405501">liter<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> tamdiu de<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>siderat<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>.</p> <closer>Vale Vir Amicissime, hilarique animo
                                    <lb/>iter tu<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> prosequere securus de mea perpetua
                                    <lb/>observantia, atque vera Amicitia. Mihi per<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>grat<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> facies, <subst><del>me admonere</del><add>si me admonebis</add></subst> de die, quo istinc
                                    <lb/>es discessurus. Vale iter<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice>; meque amare non
    <lb/>desine. <dateline><subst><del>d</del><add>D</add></subst>abam <rs type="place" key="place_VER-repven">Venetiis</rs> <date when="1719-10-06"> <choice><abbr>a. d.</abbr><expan>ad diem</expan></choice> 6 Octobris 1719.</date></dateline></closer>
    <note><note hand="pers_DE-588-119166895"><foreign xml:lang="ger"><abbr>Empf.</abbr> <abbr>d.</abbr> <date when="1719-10-07">7<hi rend="sup">ten</hi></date></foreign></note></note>
</div>
